comments: Young (TOR) lightly brushes George's (LAC) arm at the end of his drive and marginal contact occurs as he releases his pass.
George (LAC) goes to, not through, Young's (TOR) space and marginal body contact occurs thereafter the release of George's pass.
Zubac (LAC) and Young (TOR) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Young (TOR) brushes Zubac's (LAC) arm and marginal contact occurs during Zubac's play at the basket.
George (LAC) brings his arm toward Barrett's (TOR) path and marginal lower body contact occurs during Barrett's drive.
Schroder (TOR) wraps his arm around Harden's (LAC) waist off ball and the contact affects his ability to get to the pass.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in Young's (TOR) path and is firming up when marginal contact occurs as the two come together during the screen.
Schroder (TOR) places his forearm on Leonard's (LAC) side and marginal body contact occurs during Leonard's drive to the basket.
Harden (LAC) moves into Quickley's (TOR) path and initiates contact with his body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) briefly places his forearm on Barrett's (TOR) front and then immediately retracts it as he releases away and changes directions during the drive.
Zubac (LAC) places a hand on Young's (TOR) back and marginal body contact occurs during his layup attempt.
Barrett (TOR) commits a take foul on Harden (LAC).
Coffey (LAC) places his forearm to Quickley's (TOR) front and immediately slides it off as marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
